{"tid":838436,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雞蟲","createTime":"2018-09-27T06:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T07:37:30.000Z","uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf6b4ccc4ae6d164e74cc0c6708b54fc12ff48b","tid":838436,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"<strong>警方收投訴信擬派卧底查夜場 惟資金緊絀且「反黑警司」力阻未成事</strong><br />\n<br />\n有「反黑警司」之稱的港島總區刑事總部<span style=\"color: red;\">警司吳偉漢</span>，涉自2015年底起<span style=\"color: red;\">收受兩會所</span>的經營者賄款及<span style=\"color: red;\">免費嫖妓服務</span>，並向兩人洩露警方調查兩會所及行動的機密資料。吳與兩名經營者今在區院各<span style=\"color: red;\">承認一項罪名</span>。根據控方案情，警方曾接獲兩封匿名投訴電郵，直指突擊巡查只是「做大龍鳳」，涉案會所仍可繼續從事賣淫、販毒及洗黑錢勾當，月賺逾100萬元。警方一度擬派卧底調查，但因卧底行動資金緊絀，加上吳偉漢揚言不可行，故未有跟進。<br />\n<br />\n被告依次為吳偉漢（53歲）、經營MB Club Mont. Busa（MBC）及GOLDEN夜總會的欒其祥（46歲）與謝凱健（37歲）。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，吳偉漢自2015年11月29日從O記調往港島總區刑事總部，負責監督總區的反三合會行動組工作，以及監管為卧底行動提供資金的酬金及特別服務預墊備用金等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180927/58729290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58729290&d=qy6Ry%2FISLpotfIeQJdc3dwIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=8510f57d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58729290&h=ca4d33fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180927/58729290</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已讀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> too long don't read"},{"pid":"faa2d3c8b46122f723984a5339cabb009b00774a","tid":838436,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"cheating對課金用家公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁樣要成人台班食慣印賓既手足情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1389b0eff44442c2a419a08c965765c1a84aec2","tid":838436,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"阿sir叫雞唔洗你教"},{"pid":"1a805da7f28e67822f2c2b12e209504c3aacc197","tid":838436,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1389b0eff44442c2a419a08c965765c1a84aec2","tid":838436,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"阿sir叫雞唔洗你教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"以後要跟阿sir揾食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a8948d16db79225992843102c79588539ddadb","tid":838436,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91b3c5ade1e1925cca72686927339b7b6bba395","tid":838436,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"十連準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3704e2a0ebf52b70141df38fa91b8e5480e70a","tid":838436,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:32:47.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ce4479ffab839f128fa7e399ba967055117f0cfa","tid":838436,"uid":192190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:37:30.000Z","msg":"阿sir叫雞唔洗<span style=\"color: red;\"><del>你教</del></span>俾錢"}]}